{"lemma":"خَلَلَيْ","slug":"خَلَلَيْ","root":"خ.ل.ل","root_slug":"خ-ل-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/خ-ل-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":5,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":8},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n11172","n11173","n11174"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AE%D9%8E%D9%84%D9%8E%D9%84%D9%8E%D9%8A%D9%92"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to scour, to toothpick, to poke in"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to caulk"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"gap, breach, interstice, interspace, chink","examples":[{"text":"لأرى الشيطان يدخل من خلل الصف","english":"I see the Satan entering through the opening in the row"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"flaw, imbalance, bug, disturbance, trait of disorder"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"plural of خُلَّة (ḵulla)","tags":["form-of","plural"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"plural of خِلَّة (ḵilla)","tags":["form-of","plural"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to preserve in vinegar, to marinate"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to render into vinegar, to make become vinegar, to make sour"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Denominal verb of خَلّ (ḵall, “vinegar”)."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n11172","headword_ar":"خَلَلٌ","root":"xl","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An interstice, an interspace"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"intervening space, a break, a breach, a chink,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a gap, between two things;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, S, Msb, K;) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xilaAlN","text_ar":"خِلَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (JK, S, Msb:) and particularly the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"places,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"interstices,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S,) of the clouds,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from which the rain issues;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xilaAlN","text_ar":"خِلَالٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, K;) both occurring in this sense, accord. to different readings, in the Kur xxiv. 43 and xxx. 47: (S, TA:) the latter may be [grammatically] a sing. [syn. with the former], or it may be pl. of the former: (MF, TA:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ald~aAri","text_ar":"الدَّارِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xilaAlu","text_ar":"خِلَالُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what is around the limits of the house;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, K;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"around the walls thereof;"},{"kind":"text","text":"thus in the M; (TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and what is between the chambers thereof."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daxalotu bayona xalali Alqawomi","text_ar":"دَخَلْتُ بَيْنَ خَلَلِ القَوْمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xilaAlihimo","text_ar":"خِلَالِهِمْ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I entered amid the breaks,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"interspaces, of the people"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, Msb.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa xalalahumo","text_ar":"هُوَ خَلَلَهُمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xilaAlahumo","text_ar":"خِلَالَهُمْ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalaAlahumo","text_ar":"خَلَالَهُمْ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K [but in the CK these words are with damm to the second"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"l","text_ar":"ل"},{"kind":"text","text":"])"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He is amid them."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buyuwti AlH~Y","text_ar":"بُيُوتِ الحّى"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jusonaA xilaAla","text_ar":"جُسْنَا خِلَالَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"duwri Alqawomi","text_ar":"دُورِ القَوْمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xilaAla","text_ar":"خِلَالَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e. ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"We went,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"went to and fro,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"went round about, &c.,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"amid the tents of the tribe,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the midst of the houses of the people;"},{"kind":"text","text":"like a phrase in the Kur xvii. 5. (TA.) ―         -b2-  And [hence]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Shakiness, looseness, laxness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"want of compactness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"disorder,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"want of order,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a thing; (Msb;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unsoundness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"corruptness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, *) in an affair or a thing, (S,) or of a thing; (Msb;) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a flaw"},{"kind":"text","text":"in a thing;]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"defect, imperfection,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"deficiency;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ham p. 300;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"weakness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"infirmity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"in an affair, (JK, K, TA,) as though some place thereof were left uncompact, or unsound, (TA,) and in war, (JK,) and in men: (JK, K: *) and (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unsettledness"},{"kind":"text","text":"in an opinion. (K, * TA.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alxalalu","text_ar":"الخَلَلُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The night."},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, Ibn- 'Abbád.)"}],"source_refs":["JK","S","Msb","K","TA","MF","M"]},{"entry_id":"n11173","headword_ar":"خُلَلٌ","root":"xl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xulaAlapN","text_ar":"خُلَالَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n11174","headword_ar":"خِلَلٌ","root":"xl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xulaAlapN","text_ar":"خُلَالَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in three places."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}